prompts.text:
Please create a creative piece based on the following inspiration from your Obsidian vault:

## Inspiration Source:
{inspiration}

## Writing Requirements:
- Genre: {genre}
- Length: {length}
- Style: {style}
- Audience: {audience}

## Instructions:
- Use the inspiration source as a foundation for your creative work
- Maintain consistency with the established style and tone
- Develop characters, plot, or themes as appropriate for the genre
- Ensure the piece is engaging and well-structured
- Incorporate elements from your knowledge base when relevant

## Response Format:
Present your creative work in the appropriate format for the specified genre and length.
